<2zh> Niqan sediq mnarox do, mosa sapah mnarox kiya, mi smapoh, saan dha tmoty ka way mnarox sediq ka, ana mtaqi ori, tlong ori o, spohan niya. Mangal qqeyya snalo na, hbohon na poniq han, mi pstilox hiyi mnarox, kika pstilox na tonox dongan, mi kika dmoron.
